{{Top|leg}}
A '''Tendril tree''' was a large, bushy tree with a thick trunk that could be found in the tropical environs of a [[U-Tendik|nameless planet]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]. The trees yielded hand-sized edible nuts, which could be husked and used for a variety of dishes. In [[17 BBY/Legends|17 BBY]], many [[Rodian/Legends|Rodians]] of the [[Tetsu Clan]] left their [[Rodia/Legends|home planet]] and settled on this lush world to eke out a new, peaceful life for themselves. They built meager wooden huts within the branches of the Tendril trees that kept them safe from jungle predators such as the ferocious [[Manka cat/Legends|manka cat]].

